works.description:
DNA 11, the company that gave us the DNA  
Portraits and the DNA Ancestry Portraits, is now offering custom,  
one-of-a-kind waterfalls made from your DNA. The firm has already designed  
a DNA waterfall for a Manhattan client’s rooftop patio. Just imagine the  
feeling of sitting in front of a waterfall that’s made from your unique  
DNA. DNA 11 will soon start selling the DNA waterfall, along with a range  
of new custom products personalized with each customer’s unique DNA.
